## Most Important Lesson Learned

**The tool must be invisible**: Users don't want to think about formatting, fonts, margins, ATS rules, or file sizes. They want to run one command and get a perfect resume. Every design decision was made with this in mind.

**Result**: User runs one command, gets ATS-compliant resume, submits application. No thinking required.

